latestIgtvVideos.title: A Dream Dress with a bling 💫
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
We all have a dream dress somewhere hiding in our mind or in our phone gallery. We peek at it & then wonder whether it will be possible to materialise that dress. 

The same was wondered by @navneet.kaur.handa , she trusted us & got her dream dress for her Sagan 💓. She carried it like a boss. A perfect head-turner, showstopper & what-not-to-call-her!! 

Our barbie rocked the look, the wedding & couple chemistry 💕💕🤩

Bride- @navneet.kaur.handa 
Photography- @studiopepphotography
Outfit- VFS
